snippet: P.S.V. Eindhoven’s dismal season reached a new low Thursday with a 1-0 loss at home to Chornomorets Odesa in the Europa League.
abstract: PSV Eindhoven loses at home to Chornomorets Odesa 1-0, in the Europa League; other soccer news noted.
